: This article is about a 1942 telugu movie. See Bhakta Prahlada for disambiguation.

Bhakta Prahlada is a telugu movie made in 1942 by Sobhanachal banners about a devotee Prahlada in Hindu mythology. This is the second movie of the same story with more advanced technicians.

Plot
:See Narasimha#Scriptural_background|The Story of Narasimha for original story.

The movie dialog is based on the drama version used by Surabhi telugu drama troupe in those days.

Crew
* Producer - Sobhanachal productions.
* Director - Chitrapu Narayana Murthy

Cast
* Vemuri gaggaih
* Rajeswari
* Narayan Rao
* G. Varalakshmi

